{"tid":1722062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所以個熱線通過法案成件事係點呢","createTime":"2019-11-14T21:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T22:03:55.000Z","uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce852363c9c189addb7b1c237c727f792aaf9e3c","tid":1722062,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:40:07.000Z","msg":"首先講返到底有冇炒撚哂車<br />\n1.琴日晏晝睇到奶共議員頂唔住要過條法案 不過要打電話問意見 正式決定要係美國thanksgiving（11月22日）前<br />\n2.夜晚11點左右眾志突然出POST話打電話無人反對就通過法案<br />\n3.燒山漏夜出POST話今晚唔會過到<br />\n4.有POST話過左參議院過左加辣版 但係之前眾議院個版本係未加辣 所以要過多次<br />\n<br />\n我勸各位連登仔將目前情況擺返係1度<br />\n唔好係又信唔係又信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9aa97e08b500aded6a7a00e05c4497a3078fa6","tid":1722062,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:41:36.000Z","msg":"全香港連政府都炒撚哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77b76bbdde084b65c62cc2b257f53502e752029","tid":1722062,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:49:04.000Z","msg":"美國參議院外委會主席里施（Jim Risch）與參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）跟多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）見面，商討參議院表決《香港人權與民主法案》時間。麥康奈爾在香港時間凌晨約 1 時，與魯比奧就立法的建設性對話，感到鼓舞。他認為參議院應站在香港一方，希望盡快採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港眾志指出，駐華盛頓代表敖卓軒收到消息，得悉參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾 Mitch McConnell 剛剛將《香港人權及民主法案》提交大會審議，並啟動最快速的「熱線」（hotline）機制。</span>在此機制下，若在六小時內（即香港時間星期五凌晨5點前）沒有參議員反對的話，就當作一致通過《法案》的參議院版本。<br />\n<br />\n由於《法案》參眾兩院版本稍有不同，故通過參議院版本後，就會交到眾院進行多一次表決，之後便交到白宮待總統簽署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/眾志-美參院啟動-熱線-加速表決香港人權法案-或周五凌晨通過/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E9%99%A2%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95-%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%9A-%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%B1%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%88%96%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%2F&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=7e61ccab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E9%99%A2%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95-%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%9A-%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%A8%E6%B1%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%88%96%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%2F&h=f4a55e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/眾志-美參院啟動-熱線-加速表決香港人權法案-或周五凌晨通過/</a>"},{"pid":"56573e6727dd37df66276e312c518a2837493cd1","tid":1722062,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:56:13.000Z","msg":"比美國佬玩撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb419cb9bdcfb0ae99752f89f169bc5e22a7d98","tid":1722062,"uid":281189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56573e6727dd37df66276e312c518a2837493cd1","tid":1722062,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:56:13.000Z","msg":"比美國佬玩撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T22:03:55.000Z","msg":"講真美國佬算幫盡啦<br />\n你睇吓英國佬先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}